winsollib.App::__manuals [private]

The App manuals Dictionary:.

  • app_man_online - List of On-Line Manuals dictionaries.
  • app_man_online/app_man_on_name - On-Line manual name.
  • app_man_online/app_man_on_url - On-Line manual url.
  • app_man_online/app_man_on_description - On-Line manual description.
  • app_man_online/app_man_on_lang - On-Line mnuals languages.
  • app_man_offline - List of Off-Line Manuals dictionaries.
  • app_man_offline/app_man_off_name - Off-Line manual name.
  • app_man_offline/app_man_off_url - Off-Line manual url.
  • app_man_offline/app_man_off_file - Off-Line manual file name.
  • app_man_offline/app_man_off_description - Off-Line manual description.
  • app_man_offline/app_man_off_lang - Off-Line manual languages.
